Introduction

Double A was a South Korean boy group formed under Wellmade Yedang (formerly Well Made STAR M) The group made their debut on November 4th, 2011 with the song "So Crazy".

The group originally consisted of 5 members Aoora, Joowon, Woosang, Kimchi, and Hoik. Joowon left the group in June of 2013 and was later replaced by new member Jinhong.

The group disbanded in 2015.
